WEBVTT

00:00:00.547 --> 00:00:04.976
Welcome to "Five Dangerous Things
You Should Let Your Children Do."

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.976
I don't have children.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:09.310
I borrow my friends' children, so --

00:00:09.334 --> 00:00:12.548
(Laughter)

00:00:12.572 --> 00:00:14.976
take all this advice with a grain of salt.

00:00:16.345 --> 00:00:18.169
I'm Gever Tulley.

00:00:18.193 --> 00:00:22.753
I'm a contract computer
scientist by trade,

00:00:22.777 --> 00:00:26.674
but I'm the founder of something
called the Tinkering School.

00:00:27.436 --> 00:00:30.323
It's a summer program
which aims to help kids